node.text:
With Leah Wyer SVP/GM of @byrdie and Founder/ Partner  of @sblabeauty, @randishinder, and me.
I promised I would put up our #instagramlive conversation but as It was a stormy day we lost our connection ( and probably a lot of you 😉) several times so I will post the snippets we were able to salvage . And @sandylinter this one includes a shout out to legendary you. So in case you were #wand-ering …here’s a bit about #sblawands and what the silver neck chin and jawline #wand can do for you! And thank you again @leahwyar for gracing us with your presence you are pure delight! #selfcaresunday 💜💛

node.text:
With an Attitude of gratitude and @sblabeauty ‘s peptides and actives like Hyaluronic Acid Complex which delivers lipids which replenish moisture, plumps skin cells, reduces lines and wrinkles and visibly tightens the skin.
And Our SBLA Proprietary Double Peptide Blend which increases collagen production, reduces lines & wrinkles, and increases skin firmness.
Skin Repair & Brightening Blend containing Acetyl Glucosamine (Amino Acid) to moisturize, brighten & even out skin tone, repairs & treats sun damage ( hello!) while reducing age spots. 🙌🏼I’ll drink to that! Cheers! 
It also reduces puffiness & inflammation as well as tightens and firms loose skin.

See I told you, things are looking up! 
Hope you enjoyed this video which are condensed excerpts from my conversation with @breannenyc during our zoom with @womenatmeredith Thank you I loved chatting with you! 💕

Beautiful fillies at the @hamptonclassic @sailorbrinkleycook @ericapelosini @loveshackfancy 
@sblabeauty

Putting up this blooper to remind you if you missed the show you can still take advantage of @qvc’s special offers if you go to www.qvc.com and search @bellissimaprosecco 🥂🍾 
all my wines are …
#organic which means no chemicals pesticides,  herbicides,  or anything artificial from vine to bottle 
And  #vegan which means we don’t filter our  wines through animal parts like traditional wines do . 
Plus we have two which are #zerosugar #zerocarb  making them #ketofriendly 
 one is #sparklingrosé and the blue bottle is #sparklingwhite all are DELICIOUS  and pair beautifully with a #healthylifestyle‼️👍🏼🍇 #blooper 😂🤣 #wine #prosecco

node.text: @leahwyar  of @byrdie and my @sblabeauty partner @randishinder . This was an  #instagramlive that kept getting interrupted by the storm so many of you said you didn’t get a chance to see the whole thing so here’s a few more moments discussing the difference between the wands and how they can make your skin behave like you’re going to get carted when you order a Bellissima 😜 Seriously you will love the results‼️💜

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Christie Brinkley on September 01, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and people standing.

node.text:
It’s going to be a rainy night so we’re going to watch the bio-pic  @respectmovie about #arethafranklin  a woman I always respected and admired. She gave her soul to the world in every song she gifted us with. And I love #jenniferhudson too she’s so perfect for this part ( well for anything!) 
In this photo im backstage with the Queen , and she wanted to see pictures of My Princess Alexa ..naturally she ouued snd ahhed perfectly over every shot.  I just loved her. Anyway her movie is streaming on @appletv and gives me an opportunity to post this photo I cherish .

node.text:
We kind of look like a lamp store right? 
But we were actually at the annual fabulous @hamptonclassic watching the gorgeous horses jump and promoting  @equusfoundation  the only national animal welfare charity in the United States 100% dedicated to safeguarding the comfort and dignity of America's horses throughout their lives and sharing their magic and power with as many people as possible.
